node.accessibility_caption: "The Rendezook" comic by Preetom Gogoi. Page 1/4. Jet flying through the air. "Yolo commander. I'm the damn commanding officer - unit 64. What's your status? Over." Cockpit view. "Roger that, S_Gravy reporting. Zookaman on the lead. The sky looks clea... F*CK!" A bullet bounces on the wing.
Page 2/4. Two jets. "There you go soldier... yolo. YO freakin' LO!!!" A dog fight. And he's climbing?! Wait... No way...!
Page 3/4. The pilot of the climbing jet ejects. "No f*cking wayy!!! Oh... my... god!!!" The pilot has a bazooka and fires at the jet behind.
Page 4/4. Big explosion, the pilot jumps back into the jet. Only... in... Battlefield dum dum dum da dum dum...
